ent-PoliticalLoudspeaker = political loudspeaker
    .desc = A portable loudspeaker that rallies comrades.

ent-ActionPoliticalLoudspeakerHeal = Loudspeaker: Healing
    .desc = Heals allies in range.

ent-ActionPoliticalLoudspeakerSpeed = Loudspeaker: Speed
    .desc = Increases ally movement speed in range.

ent-ActionPoliticalLoudspeakerFortify = Loudspeaker: Fortify
    .desc = Reduces incoming damage for allies in range.

ent-StatusEffectPoliticalLoudspeakerSpeed = Rallying Pace
ent-StatusEffectPoliticalLoudspeakerFortify = Fortified

political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-1 = Medics to the line! No comrade will be left without aid!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-2 = Tighter bandages, steadier hearts, and back to the fight!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-3 = Head up, comrade, Soyuz medicine is already on the way!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-4 = Patch the wounds, fulfill the duty, hold the formation!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-5 = Medical tempo, comrades, heal fast and return to the line!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-6 = Pain is temporary, victory is mandatory!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-7 = Open the medkits, lift the fighters, restore order!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-8 = Healing for the masses, morale to the maximum!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-9 = Not even a scratch from the bourgeoisie can break our discipline!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-10 = Those standing help the wounded; those wounded will stand again!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-11 = We heal comrades as quickly as we defeat the enemy!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-12 = Tighten the bandages, steady the breathing, return the fighter to the line!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-13 = Every life saved brings collective victory closer!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-14 = The medical section is working, comrades, do not yield the position!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-15 = Patch the armor, mend the body, strengthen the spirit!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-16 = Recover and back to the front, the order is clear!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-17 = Wounded comrades, hold on, help is already here!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-18 = No panic, only bandages, treatment, and advance!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-19 = The Union protects its own, we heal and keep marching!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-heal-20 = Comrades, health into formation, doubts out!

political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-1 = Longer stride, comrades, it is time to outrun the enemy!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-2 = Faster to the line, discipline loves speed!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-3 = Not a second of delay, only march, only tempo!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-4 = Pick up the pace, comrades, victory does not wait for the late!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-5 = Legs to work, thoughts in order, formation forward!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-6 = Raise the tempo, close the distance, catch the enemy off guard!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-7 = Forward march, comrades, revolution favors the brisk!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-8 = Move faster, win faster!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-9 = Push harder, comrades, the slow are not written into heroics today!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-10 = Acceleration engaged, laggards not provided for!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-11 = Straight from idle to action, no delay!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-12 = Combat tempo, steady gaze, continuous movement!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-13 = Dash to the objective, comrades, and no slackness!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-14 = Whoever moves fast delivers victory first!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-15 = We found the pace and we hold it to the result!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-16 = Comrades, let the station see what organized speed looks like!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-17 = Forward faster than the rumors from cargo!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-18 = Quicken the step, strengthen the advantage!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-19 = In battle, what matters is not fuss, but a fast organized march!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-speed-20 = Run to the task, comrades, report later!

political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-1 = Hold the line, comrades, we will not be broken so easily!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-2 = Stronger stance, firmer will, not one step back!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-3 = Reinforce the line, the enemy will break before we do!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-4 = Armor of spirit higher, heads cooler, positions stronger!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-5 = Comrades, stand like a wall and do not waver!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-6 = Tighten the ranks, take the hit, preserve order!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-7 = Our endurance is tougher than enemy caliber!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-8 = Harden the formation, comrades, let the enemy break their teeth!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-9 = No panic, no disorder, only solid defense!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-10 = Shields higher, chins firmer, the line holds!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-11 = Fortification received, comrades, now try and move us!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-12 = Brace, dig in, endure the pressure!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-13 = The enemy presses, and we only grow stronger!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-14 = Do not break the line, do not abandon comrades, hold the blow!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-15 = Fortify properly, stand like a monument!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-16 = Let anything fly at us, the formation will endure!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-17 = Solid defense is an offensive too, just the clever kind!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-18 = We take the strike in an organized and dignified manner!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-19 = Clench the fist, strengthen the ranks, stand until the order comes!
political-loudspeaker-slogan-fortify-20 = A fortress is not walls, comrades, it is discipline!
